text: Sabbhineni Meghana (Born: 7 June 1996) is an Indian cricketer. She plays for Andhra women, South zone women and India women. She has played 6 WT20I, 6 First-class and 40 List A matches. She was a part of the Women's Asia Cup T20 tournament Indian team in 2016. == References == ==External links== Category:India women Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Cricketers from Andhra Pradesh Category:South Zone women cricketers Category:Andhra women cricketers Category:1996 births Category:Living people
